cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.DC

This paper discusses the use of machine learning for dynamically analyzing and classifying ransomware. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the limitations of dynamic analysis, which could place it in cs.SE (Software Engineering) or cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
